                    GitHub : <a href="https://github.com/doggang">https://github.com/doggang</a><br> 
                    Position - FrontEnd
                </div>
                <div id="footer_in">
                    Developer : Park Ju Young<br>
                    E-mail : okmlnsunok@naver.com<br>
                    GitHub : <a href="https://github.com/mythpoy">https://github.com/mythpoy</a><br> 
                    Position - BackEnd
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </footer>

</body>
<script src="/js/index_header.js"></script>
</html>